<p>[2] 海德格尔.同一与差异[M] .孙周兴等译.北京：商务印书馆，2011.</p>
<p>[3] 林治贤.伽达默尔集[C] .上海：上海远东出版社， 1997，130.</p>
<p>[4] 林治贤.伽达默尔集[C] .上海：上海远东出版社，1997，133.</p>
<p>[5] Stiegler, Bernard.1998. Technics and Time[M], vol.1: The Fault of Epimetheus. Trans.</p>
<p>Richard Beardsworth and Georges Collins. Stanford, CA:Stanford University Press</p>
